Body ♂6.0-7.0, ♀6.3-7.0; pronotum ♂4.0-4.5, ♀3.8-4.5; fore femur ♂6.8-8.0, ♀6.5-7.5; hind femur ♂10.0-11.5, ♀10.5-11.5; ovipositor 5.5-6.0.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
