<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="115" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="115">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="115">
The specific epithet refers to the shape of epiphallus, the Latin word 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="115">porta</emphasis>
meaning door.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
